    • Field Detail

      • UPDATED

        static final int UPDATED
        This interface must be implemented by objects that use the PeerList.add() and PeerList.remove() methods.

        A Peer can add another Peer to its peer list via addPeer(). All Peers in the peer list will be notified of peer changes when updateFromPeer() is called.

      • isDeaf

      • peerRemoved

        void peerRemoved​(Peer peer)
        Called when this Peer is removed from peer. Derived classes can override this method to receive direct notifications when a peer is removed.
        Parameters:
        peer - the Peer from which this Peer has been removed from notification.
